headline: West to Divest Notified
summary: ISLANDIA, N.Y., March 17, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- West Technology Group, LLC (the “Company” or “West”), a global leader in technology-enabled services, today announced it has entered into a definitive agreement to sell its Notified business to Equiniti (EQ)1, a global leader in shareholder services and advisory firm, for $534.5 million, inclusive of an $80 million earnout. Notified is a leading global technology and services partner to corporate storytellers, including investor relations (“IR”)
